file.name: Georgie Lee - Rescued from Ruin [HHS-377] (epub).epub

tika.dc.description:
What the ton doesn’t know… During the years since Randall Cheltenham,
			Marquess of Falconbridge, last saw Cecelia Thompson, he has turned into a dissolute
			rake. Catching sight of her now, bittersweet memories threaten to shatter his carefully
			constructed façade. Although in the eyes of the ton Cecelia is a wealthy widow, in
			reality she has barely a penny to her name. Randall seems to offer a safe haven, but how
			can she trust a man who has hurt her before and who seems to have only become darker
			with the passing of time?
